      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, very formal. Can you make it a bit more intense though? I want him to really lean into the idea that they're almost like children who can't govern themselves. Maybe add some descriptions of how their lifestyle seems chaotic or even dangerous compared to European standards, to justify why the \"civilizing mission\" is actually a moral necessity.",
